287
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,230
[Toko Pakaian Huajin]

288
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:25,670
Ratu,

289
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:28,110
ikat pinggang ini tidak sesuai aturan.

290
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:30,150
Bos,

291
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:32,600
