303
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,310
Chu.

304
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,609
Ini kusiapkan khusus untukmu.

305
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,740
Setelah kita menikah,

306
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,369
