308
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,800
Mewah sekali,

309
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:37,220
aku khawatir
tidak akan terbiasa tinggal di sini.

310
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,310
Chu.

311
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:44,050
